name: raj's minutes
description: The token is from timedotfun which provides creators option of creating their minutes tokens which can be used to DM the creator, voice call, phone call, and join the creators group chat. The token being called minutes is in itself explanatory, what you are buying is a creators time derived in minutes. You can get access to influencers/KOLs/founders through this platform at a price. This coin is of Raj Gokal, the Solana founder(similar to toly's minutes). A new social fi type of token.
